# Credentials — belt-and-suspenders. Nothing in Otto writes these into the
# repo today (tokens go to Keychain, configs to UserDefaults), but if you
# ever drop a sample env file or credentials JSON next to the source it
# shouldn't ride along.
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
auth.json
*.credentials.json
*.secret
*.pem
*.key

# Logs
*.log
